data.description: Discover the epitome of comfort in this 5-bedroom, 3-bath ranch-style home. With main level living, indulge in effortless luxury and convenience. Entertain in the theater room or savor culinary delights in the gourmet kitchen featuring top-notch appliances. A wet bar adds a touch of sophistication, while the 3-car heated garage ensures year-round comfort. Situated on a generous lot, this home offers space and style in one package. A ton of extras including a pool table, air hockey table, ping pong table, theater projector and popcorn machine, central vacuum system, and outdoor speakers. Your dream home awaits!
